    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You weave a distracting string of words, waving your arms to challenge a creature or otherwise get the attention of a creature.</em></p><p>A creature must be able to hear you to be affected by this spell. This spell ends if the target can no longer hear you or if you become &amp;reference[incapacitated] or &amp;reference[silenced].</p><p><strong>Wisdom Saving Throw</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[Charmed]. While charmed in this way, the target is &amp;reference[goaded] by you and has disadvantage on &amp;reference[perception] checks to locate a creature other than you. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional creature for each spell level above 2nd.</p>",
            "chat": "A creature must be able to hear you to be affected by this spell. This spell ends if the target can no longer hear you or if you become &amp;reference[incapacitated] or &amp;reference[silenced].</p><p><strong>Wisdom Saving Throw</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[Charmed]. While charmed in this way, the target is &amp;reference[goaded] by you and has disadvantage on &amp;reference[perception] checks to locate a creature other than you. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional creature for each spell level above 2nd.</p>"
        },
